name: Frame Painter for LGS Frame Set File
summary: A FRAMESET file contains a lighting animation created by J∆•Softcode Frame Painter for LGS, a program used to create animations for compatible Logitech keyboards. It stores information a frame set, which is a collection of one or more frames that make up an animation. FRAMESET files include the position and size of a .PNG, .JPG, or .GIF image keyboard overlay for each frame of the animation.
